Add @Flour{190%g} to mixing bowl.
Add @Baking Powder{16%g}.
Add @Salt{a pinch}.
Mix dry ingredients.
Crack @Egg{1}.
Add @Milk{310%ml}.
Add @Cold Melted Butter{60%g}.
Mix with fork.
Add @Vanilla Essence{1/2%teaspoon}.
Make a well in flour and pour wet ingredients inside.
Stir with no lumps.
Fry with butter, once there are bubbles at top, flip pancake.
